parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a compartment fire while the vehicle is parked or driving, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience issues with the starter and alternator
leading to difficulties in starting the vehicle. The vehicle may also shut off while driving
accompanied by unknown warning lights.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the oil pressure sensor can cause the sensor to malfunction, leading to incorrect oil pressure readings, which can result in engine damage.
symptoms: The oil pressure sensor light may come on intermittently
especially when the vehicle is at a complete stop or slowing down. The light may turn off when the vehicle begins to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS module can cause an electrical short, leading to a compartment fire while the vehicle is parked or driving, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience issues with the ABS module
leading to a risk of compartment fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the dashboard and electrical system can cause the vehicle to shut off while driving, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The dashboard may black out
and the vehicle may shut off while driving
accompanied by unknown warning lights.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the LED headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The LED headlights may turn orange
reducing visibility while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission hesitation and hard shifting can cause the vehicle to jerk or lurch, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when merging or accelerating.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates to accelerate
hard shifts
jerks or lurches while changing gears
the engine revs but does not engage
the tachometer needle swings wildly
and the vehicle slows down unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Disconnection and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission disconnection and loss of power can cause the vehicle to slow down or stall, increasing the risk of accidents or rear-end collisions.
symptoms: The vehicle turns off while driving
the engine disengages from the transmission
the tachometer behaves erratically
and all screens and electronics go dark before recovering.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Hydraulic System Recall Repair Delay
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in obtaining the necessary parts for the brake hydraulic system recall repair can lead to a potential increase in the risk of accidents or fires due to faulty brakes.
symptoms: None reported
as the issue is related to the unavailability of parts for the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake problems can cause the vehicle to catch on fire, which can lead to serious accidents or injuries.
symptoms: None reported
as the complaint is related to the recall issue and the potential risk of fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the AEB system can increase the risk of accidents, as the vehicle may not respond to emergency braking situations.
symptoms: The "Check AEB System" warning indicator illuminates
and the AEB feature does not activate in emergency braking situations.
